reviewText: Requesting a credit card from the user to allow the creation of a free AWS account sounds like a bad joke! If the account is free, why not allow the user to set-up it without providing a credit card?  They force us to provide credit card information instead of limiting our "processing usage" on AWS. If for any reason the user exceeds the usage limits, you will be automatically charged.
